extract_protocol_ch1: "Total RNA was isolated using the Trizol reagent according to the manufacturerâ€™s protocol. The quality of the RNA samples was assessed using the Bio-Rad Experion RNA StdSens analysis kit."
label_protocol_ch1: "Biotinylated, amplified cRNA was prepared from total RNA using the Illumina TotalPrep RNA Amplification Kit."
hyb_protocol: "The biotinylated cRNA was hybridized to the BeadChips per standard Illumina hybridization protocol."
scan_protocol: "The hybridized chips were stained and scanned using the Illumina HD BeadArray following the standard Illumina protocol."
data_processing: "Scanned image and bead-level data processing were performed using the Illumina BeadStudio software v3.2.
